postcontent: I have for sale a Tanfoglio Witness in 9mm (Cal. 9×19)The Tanfoglio is made in Italy and imported EAA into Rockledge, FLA. This gun is a great shooter. Magazine holds 17+1. The grip is one of the most ergonomically designed. This is a clone of the CZ75. The finish is not stainless but is called a "Wonder" Finish. It is a heat treatment to the metal to prevent corrosion, scratching, and rust. It does have a rail if you wanted to put a light or laser. Comes with original case and locks. I absolutely love this gun and the other Tanfoglio's I own; however, I couldn't pass up a deal on a model 629 and need to sell one toy to keep the next. $400 firm + transfer fee. This gun hardly looks fired. You will not be disappointed.
